text: ADIF or Adif may refer to: * Audio Data Interchange Format (ADIF), a file format to exchange Advanced Audio Coding (AAC) data; see * Adif (Administrador de Infraestructuras Ferroviarias), the state company responsible for railway infrastructure (track and stations) in Spain * Administración de Infraestructuras Ferroviarias Sociedad del Estado (ADIF), the state company responsible for railway infrastructure in Argentina
title: ADIF
